\title{Notes}
\ul{
\li{Bits UI 1.0: flexible, unstyled, accessible components for Svelte}
\li{Form \code{\startverb defaultValue\stopverb} attribute enables easy form resets}
\li{Use snippets to wrap rich HTML in custom select options}
\li{\strong{Last verified:} 2025-01-14}
}

